  "title": "Care Aide @ Upper Thomson",
  "description": "<p>The Care Aide will assist and support the training officers/staff including but not limited to:<br /></p><ul><li>Supporting the work done by the training officers/staff</li><li>Food preparation and feeding of clients</li><li>Assisting clients to walk to toilets, cleaning up and changing diapers for clients as and when necessary</li><li>Assisting in running groups, sessions, outings</li><li>Assisting staff to supervise clients (during meals or activity time)</li></ul><p>As an independent service provider, there will be no other employee benefits like leave, medical insurance or performance bonus)</p>",
