    "uen": "S93SS0060K",
    "description": "<p>SUN-DAC is a non-profit social service agency affiliated with the National Council of Social Service. It serves and cares for persons with disabilities in 3 Day Activities Centres (Upper Thomson, Choa Chua Kang &amp; Bedok South). Most of our clients are persons with moderate to severe disabilities.<br>\n<br>\nSUN-DAC mission is to help people with disabilities to live each day positively with tailored programmes of constructive activities. It also provides respite for parents and caregivers of people with disability through support and assistance services.</p>",
